config BR2_PACKAGE_BUFFER_DAEMON
	bool "buffer_daemon"
	help
	  Buffer monitoring daemon for UAC2 audio feedback control.
	  Monitors I2S playback buffer status and adjusts USB feedback
	  to maintain optimal buffer fill ratio and prevent audio delays.
	  
	  Features:
	  - Real-time buffer monitoring with 15-second averaging
	  - Hysteresis-based feedback control to prevent oscillation
	  - Gradual adjustment with configurable step size
	  - Filtering of invalid/empty buffer readings
	  - Sysfs feedback control for UAC2 gadget

	  https://github.com/PureCore/buffer_daemon